    "en": {
      "title": "A wild elephant hits actor Jackson's car",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Talawa Police say that the car in which three people including veteran actor Jackson Anthony were traveling collided with the body of a wild elephant in Moragoda area on the Anuradhapura-Talawa road.",
        "Along with the accident, the wild elephant fell on top of the cab and the vehicle was also badly damaged.",
        "A spokesperson of Anuradhapura Hospital said that Jackson Anthony, who was hospitalized, was transferred to the Colombo National Hospital for further treatment.",
        "The police say that the accident took place while returning to Anuradhapura after participating in the shooting of a TV drama in Anuradhapura.",
        "Saman Anthony and Iresh who were traveling with veteran actor Mr. Jackson Anthony have been injured in this incident.",
        "The three injured were admitted to Anuradhapura Teaching Hospital by the combination of Moragoda local residents and Talawa Police officers."
      ],
